BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Davis Farmers Market – Year-Round Fresh & Local in Central Park 
 (50th Anniversary Year!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260311T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260311T180000
UID:10000234-1773241200-1773252000@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 50 years of community and bounty at the Davis Farmer
 s Market in 2026! This iconic\, award-winning market is the heartbeat of D
 avis – bringing together local farmers\, artisans\, bakers\, food vendor
 s\, and makers every week. Wednesdays: 3:00 PM – 6:00 PM (September–Ma
 rch)\; 4:00 PM – 8:00 PM Picnic in the Park with live music (April–Aug
 ust) Shop the freshest seasonal produce\, farm-fresh eggs/meats/cheese\, a
 rtisan crafts\, hot prepared foods\, coffee\, baked goods\, and more! All 
 grown or made right here in our region. Enjoy live music (especially durin
 g summer Picnic in the Park Wednesdays)\, family activities\, SNAP matchin
 g programs\, and the lively downtown energy that makes it a favorite gathe
 ring spot for residents\, UC Davis students\, families\, and visitors. Fre
 e entry – bring your bags and support local agriculture\, sustainability
 \, and small businesses! Rain or shine\, it’s always a great day out. Sp
 ecial 2026 highlights: 50th anniversary celebrations throughout the year. 
 Don’t miss the big community event on August 1!
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-
 local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year/2026-03-11/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Davis Downtown Board Meeting
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260312T090000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260312T100000Z
UID:10000013-1773306000-1773309600@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the second Thursday of each month for our Governing
  Board of Directors meeting. The meeting is open to all interested. Stay u
 p-to-date on business and initiatives related to downtown Davis\, and the 
 opportunity to provide public comment will be available. Meetings are curr
 ently held virtually on the Zoom platform from 9:00am to 10:00am. If you a
 re interested in attending\, please contact us at info@davisdowntown.com t
 o request a Zoom meeting invitation. To view\, download and/or print Board
  of Directors meeting agendas or minutes\, click on the following link: ht
 tps://davisdowntown.com/agendas-meeting-information. Meeting locations and
  times are subject to change.
LOCATION:Davis Downtown Board Meeting\, Zoom\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-downtown-board-meeting/2026-03-1
 2/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout – Monthly Downtown Davis Art Walk & Receptio
 ns (Free!)
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T170000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T210000Z
UID:10000169-1773421200-1773435600@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Join Davis’s beloved 2nd Friday ArtAbout – a free monthly 
 self-guided artwalk coordinated by the Pence Gallery! Every second Friday\
 , stroll downtown Davis to discover fresh exhibits\, opening receptions\, 
 live music\, hands-on activities\, and direct chats with local and regiona
 l artists at 10+ galleries\, co-ops\, and businesses. Support our vibrant 
 arts scene\, uncover unique talent and styles\, and soak up the lively ene
 rgy – ideal for friends\, families\, dates\, or solo adventures. Many ve
 nues offer complimentary refreshments like wine and snacks. Free – no ti
 ckets required! Runs approximately 5:00–9:00 PM (venue receptions vary
 —check the monthly guide for specifics). Grab the printed guide (with ma
 p & details) the week of at the Pence Gallery or participating spots\, or 
 download it at pencegallery.org/events/artabout/. Interested in hosting as
  a venue\, artist\, or business? Visit https://pencegallery.org/events/art
 about/ to fill out the corresponding forms. Please submit events 3 weeks i
 n advance via the form on the site to be included in the guide and promoti
 ons. Stay in the loop: facebook.com/davisartabout Come celebrate local cre
 ativity downtown – see you on the next second Friday! 🎨✨
LOCATION:CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/2nd-friday-artabout/2026-03-13/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
